    v1 = wp.sin(tmp)
    v2 = (tmp * (wp.exp(tmp + 0.73) * (v0 + 0.30 - v0 + 0.28)))
    tmp = tmp
    v0 = ((wp.sin(v2 + 0.07) / wp.exp(v1 + 0.43)) + 0.42)
    v2 = (((v2 + 0.42 / v0 + 0.23) - (tmp + 0.22 - v0 + 0.55)) / wp.cos(0.06))
